parameters: I never thought I would be fucked by Masamune.
Well, I have quite a bit of experience myself.
So, have you accumulated enough magical power?

Well then, it's time for me to fulfill Masamune's
objective.

Mine? I've already saved Amelia. There's no need
for me to do anything more.
Are you truly satisfied with this kind of ending?

But, it's an unavoidable situation. If I can be by
Amelia's side even in this form, then it's enough.
But that's not your true feelings, right?

Perhaps you're searching for a way to start over,
aren't you?
Then why did you come back to this room again?

You probably don't accept this kind of ending at
all, do you?
There's no better outcome than this.

In Amelia's body, everything that has happened so
far is firmly remembered.
There's no point in going back...

If there's a way to make everything as if it never
happened...
It's not magic that can turn back time.

It's a magic that truly starts everything over
from the beginning.
Can you really do something like that...?

Of course. Don't underestimate me, who escaped
from the magic prison and fully revived.

By the way, Masamune's memories will also
disappear.
Don't worry. I will guide you.
Are you really going to go that far?

Ah, it's a reward for my hard work. It's fine to
have something like this.

(If you can really do it... there's no reason to
hesitate)
If that's the case... I'm counting on you.
I still like Amelia after all.

If there's still a possibility to start over, I
can't give up.

By the way, my memories will also disappear,
right?

That's sad... After all, I've been together with
Leviathan for a long time.

If we meet again, it will be my first time meeting
you.
Don't worry. We won't meet again.

Well, I am a demon after all. It would be
troublesome if I easily appeared in front of
people.
I won't be in the world after turning back time.

Using the time reversal magic and the inheritance
magic at the same time.

Inheritance magic... it's the one that transfers
magical power to a child, right?

I don't have any children. So my magical power
will disappear, but I don't know what will happen
afterwards.

That magic is originally used by kings. As a half-
demon and half-human, it probably won't activate
properly.

It wouldn't be strange for me to lose my magical
power and disappear.
Demons exist because of magical power.

There is always a consequence for the failure of
powerful magic.
There is nothing strange about it.

But if my magical power disappears, everything
will be reset.
This means we can completely start over.
Don't worry about humans and demons.
I will make sure the magic succeeds. Don't worry.

Leviathan is not a demon, human blood is also
mixed in.

In that case, the Magic Church might be able to
protect her.
Don't say stupid things, I refuse that.

I have no more attachments to this world. I have
lived for a long enough time.
Hehe. Well, it's about time to say goodbye.
This time, I will grasp happiness.
Before we part, tell me your name.

I'm sure you had a name before calling yourself
Leviathan, right?
Thank you for everything until now.
Greatland Kingdom Northern Caledonia Magic Academy
